Class CountedArtifact<T extends Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
cp213.CountedArtifact<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<CountedArtifact<T>>
public class CountedArtifact<T extends Comparable<T>> extends Object implements Comparable<CountedArtifact<T>>
Stores a artifact and an occurrence count for that artifact. The artifact must be Comparable so that it can be compared and sorted against other datas of the same type.
Version:
2025-05-04
Author:
David Brown
